  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "A voice that rings like a bell. High sync forces partial alignment while the formant shape (between I and E) adds a vocal quality to the crystalline strike. Fast attack, long decay and release create the bell envelope. Each note is simultaneously a human vowel and a metallic resonance — two things that should not coexist.",
